products.title: Cannabis sativa
products.longdescription: Cannabis sativa is an annual herbaceous flowering plant indigenous to Eastern Asia, but now of cosmopolitan distribution due to widespread cultivation. It is a recreational drug, which can be used for multiple sclerosis and nerve pain.
